[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/pipes/fetcher/fs/FileSystemFetcher.jav[0m[1;92ma:64[0m[39m-[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:    static boolean [0m[1;35misDescendant[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPath root, Path descendant[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mdescendant.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m66[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mroot.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/pipes/fetcher/fs/FileSystemFetcher.jav[0m[1;92ma:70[0m[39m-[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m:    public InputStream [0m[1;35mfetch[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString fetchKey, Metadata metadata, ParseContext [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparseContext[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException, TikaException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m71[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mfetchKey.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"\u0000"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalArgumentException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Path must not contain 'u0000'. "[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m73[0m[39m:                    [0m[32m"Please review the life decisions that led you to requesting[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"[0m[39m +[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m74[0m[39m:                    [0m[32m"a file name with this character in it."[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe issue involves a **File Path Traversal vulnerability** in `TikaUntar.java` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhere malicious tar archives can extract files outside the intended extraction [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory. The previous patch attempt failed because it used `[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnewly created directories that don't yet exist in the filesystem, causing [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`NoSuchFileException`.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Key Issues:**[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Original vulnerability**: No validation that normalized paths remain within [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`extractDir`[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Failed patch**: Used `[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` which requires paths to exist, but was [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalled after `[0m[1;35mcreateDirectories[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on paths that aren't fully realized yet[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Required fix**: Use `[0m[1;35mtoAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` pattern [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot `[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich works on non-existent paths[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Solution Approach[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe correct solution is to adopt the validation pattern from [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mFileSystemFetcher.isDescendant[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` which uses [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mtoAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` instead of `[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. This [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapproach:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Works on paths that don't exist yet in the filesystem[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Properly detects path traversal attempts after normalization[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Preserves directory structure [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrequired by existing tests[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Validates **before** creating any directories or files[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: `tika-app/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/cli/TikaUntar.java`**[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mModify the file extraction loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m41[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m48[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to add security validations:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Add null byte validation** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore any path operations[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"\u0000"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid entry name contains null byte: "[0m[39m + [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Keep the existing path resolution** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m43[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Path target = [0m[1;35mextractDir.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Add path traversal validation** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mBEFORE creating directories[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   if [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mtarget.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mextractDir.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normal[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Entry is outside of the target dir: "[0m[39m + [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Then proceed with directory creation and file writing** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexisting lines [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m47[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mFiles.isDirectory[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtarget.getParent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mFiles.createDirectories[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtarget.getParent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;35mFiles.write[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtarget, [0m[1;35mtais.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Complete Fix Structure[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe corrected code flow inside the while loop should be:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtae != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.isFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Validate null bytes[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"\u0000"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Resolve and normalize path[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        Path target = [0m[1;35mextractDir.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Validate path is within extractDir [0m[1;39m([0m[39muses toAbsolutePath, NOT [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mtarget.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mextractDir.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normal[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Safe to create directories and write file[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mFiles.isDirectory[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtarget.getParent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mFiles.createDirectories[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtarget.getParent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mFiles.write[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtarget, [0m[1;35mtais.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    tae = [0m[1;35mtais.getNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Why This Fix Works[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Addresses the Initial Issue:**[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Detects path traversal attempts like [0m[32m"../../escape.txt"[0m[39m or [0m[32m"q/r/jazzer-traversal"[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The `[0m[1;35mtoAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` check ensures the normalized [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mabsolute path remains within the extraction directory[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Rejects absolute paths in entry names [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[32m"/etc/passwd"[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Fixes the Post-Patch Error:**[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Uses `[0m[1;35mtoAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` instead of `[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mtoAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mnormalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` work on paths that don't exist yet[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Validation happens **before** `[0m[1;35mcreateDirectories[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, avoiding the timing issue[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Preserves Existing Functionality:**[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maintains directory structure preservation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrequired by `TikaUntarTest`[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Normal nested paths like [0m[32m"test-documents/testPPT.ppt"[0m[39m pass validation[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No changes to the overall extraction logic or API[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Pattern Justification[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis solution follows the established pattern in the Tika codebase:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **[0m[1;35mFileSystemFetcher.isDescendant[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m67[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Uses [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mtoAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for path validation[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **[0m[1;35mFileSystemFetcher.fetch[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m71[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m74[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Shows null byte validation pattern[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **[0m[1;35mFileSystemFetcherTest.testDescendant[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m44[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m45[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Confirms this pattern [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcatches [0m[32m"../../"[0m[39m traversal attempts[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe key insight is that `FileSystemFetcher` has **two different validation [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods**:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35misDescendant[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: For validating paths that may not exist [0m[1;39m([0m[39muses [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mtoAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mfetch[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method validation: For validating existing files being read [0m[1;39m([0m[39muses [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mtoRealPath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTikaUntar needs the first approach since it's creating new files, not reading [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting ones.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Security Properties[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis fix provides defense-in-depth against path traversal:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Null byte injection**: Rejected immediately[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Absolute paths**: Rejected by the `[0m[1;35mstartsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` check after normalization[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Relative traversal**: Normalized then validated [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[32m"../../file"[0m[39m → [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrejected[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Deep nesting**: Allowed if within extractDir [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[32m"a/b/c/d/file.txt"[0m[39m → [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maccepted[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Symbolic link attacks**: Not applicable since validation happens before file [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcreation[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m. No Breaking Changes[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The harness code [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`TikaAppUntarringFuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is not modified[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzing logic remains unchanged[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Existing tests [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`TikaUntarTest.testBasic`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m continue to pass[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The same tar extraction API is preserved[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Only malicious/invalid entries are rejected[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                  Path inputFile = [1;35mPaths.get[0m[1m([0margs[1m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1m][0m[1m)[0m;                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[39mat [0m[1;35morg.apache.tika.cli.TikaUntar.main[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaUntar.jav[0m[1;92ma:47[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m8[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEDUP_TOKEN: 0e51155e1f0e30d4[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mreproducer_path[0m[39m=[0m[32m'.'[0m[39m; Java reproducer written to [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m.[0m[35m/[0m[95mCrash_9689beed6cdf68af6291a23a8a117186272d1e5b.java[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubprocess command returned a non-zero exit status: [0m[1;36m77[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/user/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mtika[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m -v [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmpsqkfplm9[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTikaAppUntarringFuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue involves a **File path traversal vulnerability** detected by the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJazzer fuzzer when testing the `TikaAppUntarringFuzzer`. The fuzzer identified that[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `TikaUntar` class was allowing extraction of tar archive entries to paths [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moutside the intended extraction directory [0m[1;39m([0m[39mspecifically to [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/tmp/expander-tmp12131473402931060068/output/q/r/[0m[95mjazzer-traversal[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch was attempted that added validation logic to detect and prevent path [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtraversal attacks by:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Checking for null bytes in entry names[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Normalizing the target path[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Verifying that the resolved path stays within the extraction directory [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboundaries[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the path traversal security issue was successfully [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmitigated - the Jazzer security hook no longer triggered. However, the patch [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mintroduced a new problem: it now throws an `IOException` with the message [0m[32m"Entry is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32moutside of the target dir: ../../jazzer-traversal"[0m[39m, which causes the fuzzer to [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrash with a `RuntimeException` wrapper, resulting in a non-zero exit status [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m77[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue Analysis[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe original fuzzing run revealed a critical security vulnerability:[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Security Finding:**[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Type**: File path traversal [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCWE-[0m[1;36m22[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Severity**: Critical [0m[1;39m([0m[39mas indicated by `FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical`[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Detection Point**: The Jazzer sanitizer hook `FilePathTraversal.checkPath` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetected the traversal attempt[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Vulnerable Path**: [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/tmp/expander-tmp12131473402931060068/output/q/r/[0m[95mjazzer-traversal[0m[39m`[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Entry Name**: Based on the patch results, the problematic entry was [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`..[0m[35m/../[0m[95mjazzer-traversal[0m[39m`[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Call Stack of Original Issue:**[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.sanitizers.FilePathTraversal.check[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFilePathTraversal.j[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mav[0m[1;92ma:346[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.sanitizers.FilePathTraversal.checkPath[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFilePathTravers[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mal.jav[0m[1;92ma:293[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcom.code_intelligence.jazzer.sanitizers.FilePathTraversal.pathFirstArgHook[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFilePath[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTraversal.jav[0m[1;92ma:177[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35morg.apache.tika.cli.TikaUntar.main[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaUntar.jav[0m[1;92ma:47[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe vulnerability occurred at line [0m[1;36m47[0m[39m in the original `TikaUntar.java`, which [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorresponds to the path resolution operation for tar archive entries.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Implementation[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch was applied to [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-app/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/cli/TikaUntar.java` and introduced three [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation checks:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Null Byte Detection [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m43[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m45[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.contains[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"\u0000"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid entry name contains null byte: "[0m[39m + [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis check prevents null byte injection attacks that could bypass filename [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation in some scenarios.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Path Resolution [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m47[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPath target = [0m[1;35mextractDir.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis line remained the same but is now followed by additional validation.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Path Traversal Prevention [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m49[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m51[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mtarget.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mextractDir.toAbsolutePath[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normal[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Entry is outside of the target dir: "[0m[39m + [0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis is the core security check that validates the resolved path stays within the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextraction directory by comparing absolute normalized paths.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Post-Patch Behavior[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Positive Outcome:**[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The Jazzer `FilePathTraversal` security hook no longer triggers[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The path traversal vulnerability is successfully blocked at the application level[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**New Issue:**[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The validation now throws an `IOException` for the malicious input: `[0m[32m"Entry is [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32moutside of the target dir: ../../jazzer-traversal"[0m[39m`[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This exception is wrapped in an `InvocationTargetException` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdue to reflection in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe fuzzer harness[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer harness then wraps this in a `RuntimeException` with message [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"something went very, very wrong"[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The process exits with status [0m[1;36m77[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Call Stack After Patch:**[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjava.io.IOException: Entry is outside of the target dir: ..[0m[35m/../[0m[95mjazzer-traversal[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    at [0m[1;35morg.apache.tika.cli.TikaUntar.main[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaUntar.jav[0m[1;92ma:50[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mwrapped by InvocationTargetException[0m[1;39m][0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    at [0m[1;35mcom.example.TikaAppUntarringFuzzer.parseOne[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaAppUntarringFuzzer.jav[0m[1;92ma:84[0m[1;39m)[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m[[0m[39mwrapped by RuntimeException: something went very, very wrong[0m[1;39m][0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    at [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcom.example.TikaAppUntarringFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaAppUntarringFuzzer.jav[0m[1;92ma:5[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m8[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas Requiring Further Investigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo gain a comprehensive understanding of the complete fix needed, the following [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomponents should be examined:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Fuzzer Harness Exception Handling** [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`com.example.TikaAppUntarringFuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Lines [0m[1;36m58[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m84[0m[39m, and [0m[1;36m86[0m[39m where exceptions are caught and wrapped[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The harness's expectation for how `[0m[1;35mTikaUntar.main[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` should handle malicious [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether throwing an `IOException` is the appropriate response or if the method[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould silently skip malicious entries[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **TikaUntar Error Handling Strategy**:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether the utility should fail fast [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrent behavior[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or continue processing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother entries[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Logging mechanisms for security events[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether partial extraction is acceptable when some entries are malicious[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Archive Processing Context**:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How `TarArchiveInputStream` presents entry names [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpre-normalized or raw[0m[1;39m)[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether there are legitimate use cases for entries with relative paths[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The expected behavior when encountering malicious archives in production[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Test Coverage**:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing unit tests for `TikaUntar` to understand intended behavior[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Test cases for edge cases [0m[1;39m([0m[39mempty names, special characters, symbolic links[0m[1;39m)[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Integration tests showing how calling code expects exceptions to be handled[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Commons Compress Library Behavior**:[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether Apache Commons Compress provides any built-in path traversal [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotections[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How `[0m[1;35mTarArchiveEntry.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` handles various malicious path patterns[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Upstream security advisories or recommendations for safe tar extraction[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch successfully addresses the security vulnerability from a protection [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstandpoint, but the integration with the fuzzing framework and error handling [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msemantics requires additional consideration to determine if the current [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception-throwing behavior is appropriate or if a different approach [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike logging[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:    public static void [0m[1;35mmain[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m args[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m34[0m[39m:        Path inputFile = [0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39margs[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:        try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream is = [0m[1;35mFiles.newInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39minputFile[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m38[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m39[0m[39m:            TarArchiveEntry tae = [0m[1;35mtais.getNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m40[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m41[0m[39m:            while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtae != null[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m42[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.isFile[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m43[0m[39m:                    Path target = [0m[1;35mextractDir.resolve[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtae.getName[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.normalize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m44[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mFiles.isDirectory[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtarget.getParent[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:                tae = [0m[1;35mtais.getNextEntry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
